message.body: Hey hunter- it's Emily. I found your carhartt hat at my house. Let me know if you want to swing by for it or if I can drop it off somewhere for you.

Oh great! I have a spare so my ears aren't currently frozen and it's no rush to get it back. If I'm gonna be in your hood I'll let u know or if you see Michael sometime just give it to him . Happy new year!
Sounds good. Happy new year to you too!
